Returns: Buffer containing the @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppState_E@ objects for this app. Guaranteed to be non-null, but may be empty.

ClassDesc: Result delivered when app state data has been loaded. Possible status codes include: @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppStateStatusCodes#STATUS_OK_E@ if data was successfully loaded and is up-to-date. @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppStateStatusCodes#STATUS_NETWORK_ERROR_NO_DATA_E@ if the device was unable to communicate with the network and has no local data available. @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppStateStatusCodes#STATUS_NETWORK_ERROR_STALE_DATA_E@ if the device was unable to retrieve the latest data from the network. @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppStateStatusCodes#STATUS_CLIENT_RECONNECT_REQUIRED_E@ if the client needs to reconnect to the service to access this data. @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppStateStatusCodes#STATUS_INTERNAL_ERROR_E@ if an unexpected error occurred in the service.
